<font color="yellow">Aey, malam-malam begini sedang apa di sini, Geomsanim?</font>

3
00:00:27,778 --> 00:00:30,480
<font color="yellow">Aey, Nam Hyeongsa juga sedang apa di sini?</font>

4
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,382
<font color="yellow">Aku dikirim oleh Geomsajang ke sini.</font>

5
00:00:32,382 --> 00:00:35,252
<font color="yellow">Aey, aku dapat telepon kalau Jo Soo Ji muncul.</font>

6
00:00:35,252 --> 00:00:37,087
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak dengar soal itu.</font>

7
00:00:37,087 --> 00:00:39,856
<font color="yellow">Auh, dari mana kau dengar kabar burung begitu?</font>

8
00:00:39,856 --> 00:00:42,192
<font color="yellow">Ah, benar juga.</font>

9
00:00:42,292 --> 00:00:45,062
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah memeriksa sekeliling,
