<font color="yellow">Aku yakin para reporter akan menempelinya beberapa hari.</font>

142
00:11:07,717 --> 00:11:09,585
<font color="yellow"><i>Ibu Jo Soo Ji saat ini...</i></font>

143
00:11:09,585 --> 00:11:12,021
<font color="yellow">- Tidak pergi? Tidak pergi?
- Astaga!</font>

144
00:11:12,021 --> 00:11:15,191
<font color="yellow">Pergi! Pergi! Apa yang kalian lakukan di depan tokoku?</font>

145
00:11:17,994 --> 00:11:19,362
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja, dia ibuku.</font>

146
00:11:21,464 --> 00:11:23,199
<font color="yellow">Dia membuat takut para reporter.</font>

147
00:11:26,202 --> 00:11:28,805
<font color="yellow">Dia tampak terlalu sehat bagi para reporter
untuk disebut sedang sakit.</font>

148
00:11:28,805 --> 00:11:29,872
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu...</font>

149
00:11:29,872 --> 00:11:32,875
<font color="yellow">...rencana untuk menjebak kita menggunakan media,
rencananya Yoon Seung Ro...</font>

150
00:11:32,875 --> 00:11:34,177
<font color="yellow">...sudah sepenuhnya gagal, 'kan?</font>

151
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:39,716
<font color="yellow">Apa kita ikuti rencananya saja?</font>

152
00:11:40,149 --> 00:11:42,118
<font color="yellow">- Apa maksudmu?
- Nam Hyeongsa yang kumaksud.</font>

153
00:11:43,119 --> 00:11:44,887
<font color="yellow">Ayo kita jebak dia dengan berita palsu.</font>

154
00:11:54,464 --> 00:11:55,798
<font color="yellow">Oh, halo.</font>

155
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,667
<font color="yellow">Sudah lama sekali, ya.</font>

156
00:11:58,367 --> 00:11:59,635
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana tercekiknya hidup sebagai detektif?</font>

157
00:11:59,635 --> 00:12:02,138
<font color="yellow">Aey, tetap saja ini sumber penghasilanku.</font>

158
00:12:02,138 --> 00:12:04,841
<font color="yellow">Oh, ini dia.
Laporan yang semalam kau minta.</font>

