<font color="yellow">Dia membaca artikelnya, berarti ada sesuatu.</font>

171
00:13:07,970 --> 00:13:10,740
<font color="yellow">Mungkin dia hanya penasaran, kita tunggu saja.</font>

172
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:17,246
<font color="yellow">(Reporter Ji Seung Hyun dari Surat Kabar Ilseong)</font>

173
00:13:26,322 --> 00:13:28,391
<font color="yellow">Ah, ya, dengan Surat Kabar Ilseong?</font>

174
00:13:28,891 --> 00:13:31,994
<font color="yellow">Ah, aku PD dari MBS.</font>

